-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-
                             General
         Armera is a text based adventure/exploration game.
      your character begins in the middle of a barren wasteland
              having no memory of how they got there,
      they begin a journey filled with discovery and adventure

                            1:Back
