                             Setup
              Before our adventurer starts their journey
                we need a little information from you

                  What is our adventurers name?


        How sturdy is our adventurer | think strength/endurance

      How acute is our adventurer | think intelligence/perception

            How endearing is our adventurer, think charisma

                      How Lucky is our adventurer
                                 0-10
                  What is our adventurers gender
              1:Male         2:Female        3:Non-binary

