-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-
                        General Controls
  these are used for movement on the map [up, down, right, left]
  to view stats and your inventory type "menu"
  in the inventory type the number next the the items name to use it
  to search for loot or quests at the players position use "check"
  all other inputs are numbered, just type the number of your choice
                like this->  1:Back
